instructions.usage: This list is designed for bulk pre-generation of AI examples at A1, B1, and C1 levels
instructions.processing: Process in batches of 50-100 words to avoid rate limiting
instructions.resumable: Script tracks progress and can resume from last successful batch
notes: Top 150 words shown here as reference
Full list of 5,000 words should be sourced from authoritative frequency corpora
For production use, integrate actual frequency lists from SpanishInput or WordFrequency.info
Current subset prioritizes: verbs (50), articles/prepositions (20), common nouns (50), adjectives (15)
